{"tid":2495911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：北區醫院54歲男子昏迷搶救後不治　本月2日接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T02:56:22.000Z","uid":290404,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"41dda8ef107d5e7830589cb968a4588f69ffe392","tid":2495911,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"RTHK連科興個名都唔提<br />\n<br />\n北區醫院表示，一名54歲男子昨日凌晨被發現昏迷，由救護車送到該院急症室，經搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n院方表示，病人在入院前16日、<strong>本月2日曾接種新冠病毒疫苗</strong>，院方昨日已按機制將個案呈報衞生署。<br />\n<br />\n公立醫院醫護人員會根據機制向衞生署呈報符合接種新冠疫苗嚴重或非預期異常事件的求診個案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586600-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586600-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=af7fa4bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586600-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e9a9ac21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586600-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"028becdacca75ba076f28fe782bdb580a77d465d","tid":2495911,"uid":88860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d6971e2f95d1e41cbff622b4b633d7064a4e21","tid":2495911,"uid":36157,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"提咩本月2日唧？<br />\n就算係本世紀第２日打都唔關事架啦"},{"pid":"7cbd77052708ca93e371177f3c9ff5b26cf993a4","tid":2495911,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"有無法國呢排打完疫苗RIP左或者入左院果D人......<br />\n<br />\n都無提過打左邊隻疫苗......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58686c11c11cbeff6efdf7f155f3a152aa9241f7","tid":2495911,"uid":76310,"like":5,"dislike":0,